    hadithEnglish:
      ' Narrated Abu Huraira:\n\nAbu Bakr said, By Allah! If they (pay me the Zakat and) withhold even a she-kid which they used to pay during the lifetime of Allahs Messenger (ﷺ), I will fight with them for it. `Umar said, It was nothing but Allah Who opened Abu Bakrs chest towards the decision to fight, and I came to know that his decision was right.',
