      ' Narrated Sa`id bin Jubair:\n\nIbn `Umar used to oil his hair. I told that to Ibrahim who said, What do you think about this statement: Narrated Aswad from `Aisha: As if I were now observing the glitter of the scent in the parting of the hair of the Prophet (ﷺ) while he was Muhrim?',
