      ' Narrated Ibn `Abbas:\n\nI gave Zamzam water to Allahs Messenger (ﷺ) and he drank it while standing. Asia (a sub-narrator) said that `Ikrima took the oath that on that day the Prophet (ﷺ) had not been standing but riding a camel.',
