    hadithEnglish:
      ' Narrated `Abdullah bin Mas`ud:\n\nI offered (only a) two rak`at prayer with the Prophet (at Mina), and similarly with Abu Bakr and with `Umar, and then you d offered in opinions. Wish that I would be lucky enough to have two of the four rak`at accepted (by Allah).',
