    hadithEnglish:
      ' Narrated Ibn `Abbas:\n\nThe Prophet (ﷺ) was asked by a man who said, I have done the Rami in the evening. The Prophet (ﷺ) replied, There is no harm in it. Another man asked, I had my head shaved before the slaughtering. The Prophet (ﷺ) replied, There is no harm in it.',
