    hadithEnglish:
      ' Narrated Abu Huraira:\n\nThe Prophet (ﷺ) said, None of you should fast a day or two before the month of Ramadan unless he has the habit of fasting (Nawafil) (and if his fasting coincides with that day) then he can fast that day.',
