      ' Narrated Abu Usama from Hisham bin Urwa from Fatima:\n\nAsma bint Abi Bakr said, We broke our fast during the lifetime of the Prophet (ﷺ) on a cloudy day and then the sun appeared. Hisham was asked, Were they ordered to fast in lieu of that day? He replied, It had to be made up for. Ma`mar said, I heard Hisham saying, I dont know whether they fasted in lieu of that day or not.',
