    hadithEnglish:
      ' Narrated Ziyad bin Jubair:\n\nA man went to Ibn `Umar I. and said, A man vowed to fast one day (the sub-narrator thinks that he said that the day was Monday), and that day happened to be `Id day. Ibn `Umar said, Allah orders vows to be fulfilled and the Prophet (ﷺ) forbade the fasting on this day (i.e. Id).',
