      ' Narrated Ibn `Umar:\n\n`Umar asked the Prophet (ﷺ) I vowed in the Pre-Islamic period of ignorance to stay in I`tikaf for one night in Al-Masjid al-Haram. The Prophet (ﷺ) said to him, Fulfill your vow.',
