      ' Narrated Jabir:\n\nWhile we were offering the prayer with the Prophet (ﷺ) a caravan carrying food came from Sham. The people looked towards the caravan (and went to it) and only twelve persons remained with the Prophet. So, the Divine Inspiration came; But when they see some bargain or some amusement, they disperse headlong to it. (62.11)',
