    hadithEnglish:
      ' Narrated `Abdullah bin `Umar:\n\nAisha, (mother of the faithful believers) wanted to buy a slave girl and manumit her, but her masters said that they would sell her only on the condition that her Wala would be for them. `Aisha told Allahs Messenger (ﷺ) of that. He said, What they stipulate should not hinder you from buying her, as the Wala is for the manumitted.',
